Package: qRAT
Type: Package
Title: qPCR Relative Expression Analysis Tool
Version: 0.6.0
Author: Daniel Flatschacher [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Daniel Flatschacher <daniel.flatschacher@uibk.ac.at>
Description: An R-based standalone application to automate the processing of 
    raw Quantification Cycle (Cq) data files. It provides a comprehensive 
    solution for relative quantification (delta-delta Cq) including 
    inter-plate calibration, reference gene stability analysis (geNorm), 
    and publication-ready visualizations.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
